strings: <voice_0x01000D84><se_low>January: Hi, it's been a long time, are you finally home?
<voice_0x01000D85><se_def>checked: Come see who it is! Will you come over when I'm gone, boy? sorry i wasn't there
<voice_0x01000D86><se_def>checked: But if I come back, and my memory serves me well, do you need the info?
<voice_0x01000D87><se_low>January: I'm looking for someone who has a big brain and is funny. Her name is Pride.
<voice_0x01000D88><se_low>January: You are a fraud buyer, please stay away from us. Did you hear something?
<voice_0x01000D89><se_def>checked: Here is what I heard. Abe Chalk's killer is none other than...
<voice_0x01000D8A><se_def>checked: My sources say they saw her in the North Sea.
<voice_0x01000D8B><se_low>January: What about Westeros Just like "Asaki", right? Would you like to know more?
<voice_0x01000D8C><se_def>checked: I'm sorry, that's all I know. I hope that you can tell me more.
<voice_0x01000D8D><se_low>January: If you don't understand the brain, you don't need to know anything. We're heading west.
<voice_0x01000D8E><se_def>checked: Good idea, I've forgotten how to cross the sea.
<voice_0x01000D8F><se_low>January: ... ... rig?
<voice_0x01000D90><se_def>checked: All flights to the north of the mainland were recently canceled due to an increase in sea monster attacks.
<voice_0x01000D91><se_def>checked: If you have your own boat you can go there. But you wouldn't have gone if I hadn't told you such a terrible thing.
<voice_0x01000D92><se_low>January: Hmm... never would have thought of that.
<voice_0x01000D93><se_def>checked: It doesn't work, in my opinion. Maybe I can help you with what I've heard from you.
<voice_0x01000D94><se_def>checked: Follow the coastal cliffs west of Prospect Harbor to the Sahara.
<voice_0x01000D95><se_def>checked: I heard there's a shipwreck there.
<voice_0x01000D96><se_def>checked: I don't know why this ship can swim without water, but then again... some say it is a magic ship.
<voice_0x01000D97><se_def>checked: If I can go back to work, I can go anywhere.
<voice_0x01000D98><se_def>checked: You can also try the route west of Prospect Harbor. It was closed to traffic due to a landslide, but as far as I can tell it was destroyed.
